      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/19a9297902c06beac6e5800d74bf3368/ff4868b842ae2b67-56/s640x960/932538d181c75477a7f328c708b6a5acc5acb132.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"722\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\"A publisher's office. A writer and editor meet. &#10;&#10;&quot;I wasn't entirely convinced by the portrayal of thugs, hoodlums and henchmen in your novel, Quentin.&quot; Says the editor holding the manuscript, &quot;So I've brought in an insensitivity reader.&quot;&#10;&#10;The writer looks nervously at an enormous, muscular, tattoed, stubbly, shaven-headed, man who holds the manuscript, a tiny pen, and grins with (perhaps unintentional) menace.&#10;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/19a9297902c06beac6e5800d74bf3368/ff4868b842ae2b67-56/s75x75_c1/fe6f68a303fcecb2d51b8bc7df3c1ff0e6cbf9d1.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/19a9297902c06beac6e5800d74bf3368/ff4868b842ae2b67-56/s100x200/916b13a74b31736c2d1d1a946c16721d518a6e85.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/19a9297902c06beac6e5800d74bf3368/ff4868b842ae2b67-56/s250x400/c2036096ab8704ce5229f3751ba0bc407293ac05.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/19a9297902c06beac6e5800d74bf3368/ff4868b842ae2b67-56/s400x600/d584e8236d8825ac2e51831821a02c59d977ca60.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/19a9297902c06beac6e5800d74bf3368/ff4868b842ae2b67-56/s500x750/6d3fa270d238ec2bafdf14fc5e869251e53841de.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/19a9297902c06beac6e5800d74bf3368/ff4868b842ae2b67-56/s540x810/923ba6265734689312f88e5ba5886655d0cfef35.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/19a9297902c06beac6e5800d74bf3368/ff4868b842ae2b67-56/s640x960/932538d181c75477a7f328c708b6a5acc5acb132.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/19a9297902c06beac6e5800d74bf3368/ff4868b842ae2b67-56/s1280x1920/1aaf39e1cfcb018853debe212cc0cb6fa699062f.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/>"
