    {
      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/811701226883416064",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/811701226883416064",
      "title": "A spring cartoon for New Scientist ",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d4d23f2f44ccfb484f68d16b91e81124/4571c0a1d1f1e9ee-ee/s640x960/1d11fa669adbbedaef241ee023fb357ec173a2eb.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"804\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\"A three panel cartoon. Two scientists walk across a green campus towards their lab. Across the three panels the season changes from winter to spring. In the third panel one of them says &quot;That guy is one VERY committed botanist!&quot; At the bottom of the panel is a balding bespectacled scientist making notes while staring at a daffodil. His whole body, except his head, shoulders and forearms, is buried in the ground.  Looking back at the previous panels reveals that he has risen out of the ground along with the daffodils: in the first just his bald head amongst the daffodils greens, in the second as the flowers emerge so does his head.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d4d23f2f44ccfb484f68d16b91e81124/4571c0a1d1f1e9ee-ee/s75x75_c1/e5ecb05d4641cf5fa220b79cec21acb31bc5e4d1.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d4d23f2f44ccfb484f68d16b91e81124/4571c0a1d1f1e9ee-ee/s100x200/22c69685ab3f98b59bb819b19d33795150c8f145.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d4d23f2f44ccfb484f68d16b91e81124/4571c0a1d1f1e9ee-ee/s250x400/dd86cf624f1ae7613ce6c63e7b4f56d102a4759c.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d4d23f2f44ccfb484f68d16b91e81124/4571c0a1d1f1e9ee-ee/s400x600/0ab4c0f0dcf3a4019ffdeb766b8540d04afc8e5e.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d4d23f2f44ccfb484f68d16b91e81124/4571c0a1d1f1e9ee-ee/s500x750/9ff358e79eb3ae0a35ca6ba2b343b31e5741e86f.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d4d23f2f44ccfb484f68d16b91e81124/4571c0a1d1f1e9ee-ee/s540x810/11829ab6916fd98152f1467d2ccf344758fb86fa.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d4d23f2f44ccfb484f68d16b91e81124/4571c0a1d1f1e9ee-ee/s640x960/1d11fa669adbbedaef241ee023fb357ec173a2eb.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d4d23f2f44ccfb484f68d16b91e81124/4571c0a1d1f1e9ee-ee/s1280x1920/9ac426e16a2a434010693df876f3423c8f